            The first step to solving a social issue is to understand it.</li>
            <li style="text-align: justify; margin-left:10%; margin-right:10%;padding-bottom:1%;">   We FoodCare invites you to be a part of our effort to understand the reality of malnutrition in India and
            discuss ways you and we can be part of the solution. </li>
            <li style="text-align: justify; margin-left:10%; margin-right:10%;padding-bottom:1%;">   Help us in creating an awareness campaign on redistributing excess food to needy people and remove hunger
