        <li style="text-align: justify; margin-left:10%; padding-right:10%;padding-bottom:1%;" >Everyone should follow proper food hygiene and quality checks at the point of
            collection, transportation and distribution of fresh or surplus cooked food.
        </li>
        <li style="text-align: justify; margin-left:10%; padding-right:10%;padding-bottom:1%;">
            Ensure about expiry products are not expired before collecting them from donors
            Once you reach the feed spot (slum areas) - take a pause, meet the beneficiaries, speak with them, give them the food.
        </li>
         <li style="text-align: justify; margin-left:10%; padding-right:10%;padding-bottom:1%;">
